import React from 'react'
import { Button } from '../../'
import * as s from './Footer.elements'

export const Footer = () => {
    return (
        <s.FooterContainer>
            <s.FooterSubscription>
                <s.FooterSubheading>
                    Subscribe to our exclusive newsletter to be the most up-to-date 
                    with the latest spaceship technology news.
                </s.FooterSubheading>
                <s.FooterSubText>
                    You can unsubscribe from this newslwtter at any time.
                </s.FooterSubText>
                <s.Form>
                    <s.FormInput name='email' type='email' placeholder='Your Email'>
                        <Button fontBig>Subscribe</Button>
                    </s.FormInput>
                </s.Form>
            </s.FooterSubscription>
        </s.FooterContainer>
        
    )
}
